// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2544 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 02bcf8ec-2cc6-5ae4-9cda-b12ce64fbdd1

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
